high_descs: Turn around and go near the pan.
Pick up the pan from the sink.
Turn right and again turn right and go near the fridge.
Wash the pan in dish washer and take it out.
Move little forward and turn left, then go near the cabinet.
Keep the pan inside the cabinet under the oven.
anns.task_desc: Wash the hexagon pan in sink in dish washer and keep it in the cabinet under the oven.

high_descs: Turn your left and move towards the pan.
Take the pan from the stove.
Turn back and walk towards the fridge on your right side.
Open the fridge door and place the pan into the fridge and close the door. Again open the door and take the pan and close the door.
Turn your left and move towards the cabinet and open the cabinet door.
Place the pan in the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn left to reach the sink.
Pick up the pan on the right of the sink.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the pan in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to reach the cabinet.
Put the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pan in the cabinet.
